{"tid":775494,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★黃雨「淋穿」2港鐵站　月台現瀑布大堂變水塘","createTime":"2018-08-11T08:11:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T16:57:38.000Z","uid":19454,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"125ee4e56daba0ce45add5520970d6f393dbff7d","tid":775494,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:11:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180811/photo/bkn-20180811114609763-0811_00822_001_01b.jpg?20180811155629\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180811%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180811114609763-0811_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20180811155629&h=442f22bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n醜聞纏身的港鐵竟不敵「黃雨」來襲，今日(11日)至少2個港鐵站出現「室內落雨」情況。有網民今早在社交網站上載影片，東鐵太和站一個月台牆身出現嚴重漏水，疑似由天花板漏出，並形成小型瀑布，雨水傾瀉程度與外間的大雨不相上下，令月台地面出現大攤積水。東網今早亦收到讀者報料，西鐵元朗站大堂亦出現大範圍漏水，地面濕漉漉，港鐵出動近20名職員幫忙拖地，場面墟冚。<br />\n<br />\n網民Siu Yuen今早8時在Facebook群組「Tai Po 大埔」上載影片，太和站的月台地面出現大攤積水，幸好是日周末，否則在繁忙時間大批乘客上落，容易造成「跣倒」等安全問題。另有讀者早上8時許在元朗站拍攝到該站大堂出現大面積漏水，多名港鐵職員忙於拖地清理積水，並用沙包堆放在大堂的商舖門口。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民擔心港鐵室內漏水會引起漏電問題，促港鐵盡快處理，但有網民就批評港鐵車費年年加，醜聞及管理不善等問題卻日日新鮮；有網民更暗諷港鐵「周圍火頭」，無暇理會漏水等小事。<br />\n<br />\n港鐵今午回覆指，職員今早8時許發現太和站二號月台近第八卡車廂位置的天花漏水，已即使安排職員跟進及清潔地面積水，並用廣播通知乘客小心地滑，事件未對列車服務構成影響。港鐵相信是大暴雨令天花板的縫隙漏水，工程人員正密切觀察，待稍後天氣穩定便進行修補工作。至於元朗站情況，港鐵尚未回覆。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180811/bkn-20180811114609763-0811_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180811%2Fbkn-20180811114609763-0811_00822_001.html&d=GJcPMEruID2M0yd6UrIIRsn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=637270a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180811/bkn-20180811114609763-0811_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4a6472cf82b0e74ec1ba4055c0ae8a6732a12f3b","tid":775494,"uid":19454,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:12:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180811/photo/bkn-20180811114609763-0811_00822_001_04b.jpg?20180811155629\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180811%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180811114609763-0811_00822_001_04b.jpg%3F20180811155629&h=ac0cd9c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1b4eae31e4660a8c5057b65d9772deb0f597f053","tid":775494,"uid":177089,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:12:43.000Z","msg":"港鐵末日"},{"pid":"9810ea910dada8f362aa50ff719af8a1659c5f51","tid":775494,"uid":44171,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:13:33.000Z","msg":"其實班人係地鐵玩冰壺姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0e17b7e0d5cfa9249ac9d49138b86940e51553b","tid":775494,"uid":158977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:14:00.000Z","msg":"馬俊偉游水.jpg"},{"pid":"27c3a980ec87060e26e3705876d14de0d070d1e2","tid":775494,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:14:29.000Z","msg":"水舞天下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15cfb49f96a771052ed5c432ab44549c90afd7ed","tid":775494,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:15:21.000Z","msg":"以後夾埋天文台 一有咩翻風落雨就掛十號波黑雨 咁咪有借口囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68aeeffb30e53b65449daafa15f24b6c81cd3ff5","tid":775494,"uid":36478,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"713c2773dd5b7cba92932d48a5d693c7f458e282","tid":775494,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:21:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8fbbf1679d7e2f96ee9a0231350cf1143fb2b77e","tid":775494,"uid":24660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T08:30:28.000Z","msg":"你身為鐵膠，點睇"},{"pid":"ca2c08f94662c62b44631163b218aa0e7f04650d","tid":775494,"uid":26752,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score